description:
Early Adopter Bonus
-----
Limited-edition Rogue: Yatabushi
The result of many a mechanic's efforts in fusing together multiple Rogue armors, with an emphasis placed on weight and sturdiness. Its form factor is based on the armor of Japanese warriors from long ago.
-----
This bonus is only available to those who purchase before 11:59 p.m.  on May 31, 2024.
